 &reftitle.resources;
 &no.resource;





 Security consideration


  This extension need administrator's privilegies for some actions as 
  create, 
  delete, 
  start, 
  stop, 
  pause, 
  continue.
  This requirement can provide an elevation of privilegies if the service 
  control is available from web interface or remote control.



  You can set the ACL on the service after add into SCM for delegate the 
  currents administrations tasks to an non administrator account or service account.
  See for more 
  instructions.
